OL,3,CMan suffers 'life-changing' injury in
OL,4,CNewtownards crash
OL,6,FA man aged in his 30s has suffered a
OL,7,F"life-changing limb injury" in a crash
OL,8,Fin Co Down.
OL,10,FThe incident took place at Castlebawn
OL,11,FRetail Park in Newtownards at around
OL,12,F1.20pm on Saturday.
OL,14,FPolice said the man was reported to
OL,15,Fhave been struck by a blue Skoda
OL,16,FOctavia and appealed for information.
OL,26,@oD@AOUoD@[O]
