OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1779646268
OL,3,CMan suffers 'life-changing' injury in
OL,4,CNewtownards crash
OL,6,FA PSNI Spokesperson said: "Officers
OL,7,Fattended the scene of a collision at
OL,8,FCastlebawn Retail Park at around
OL,9,F1.20pm, after a pedestrian was
OL,10,Freported to have been struck by a blue
OL,11,FSkoda Octavia," said local policing
OL,12,FSergeant Young.
OL,14,F"A white Vauxhall Astra parked nearby
OL,15,Falso sustained damage.
OL,26,@nD@[OUsD@OO]vD@AOU
