PN,44303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1779646268
OL,3,CMan suffers 'life-changing' injury in
OL,4,CNewtownards crash
OL,6,F"Colleagues from the Northern Ireland
OL,7,FAmbulance Service and Air Ambulance
OL,8,Fattended and the pedestrian, a man
OL,9,Faged in his 30s, was taken to hospital
OL,10,Ffor treatment to a life-changing limb
OL,11,Finjury.
OL,13,F"Inquiries are ongoing and we would
OL,14,Fappeal to anyone who may have
OL,15,Fwitnessed the collision, particularly
OL,16,Fthose who may have dash-cam or other
OL,17,Ffootage, to contact police on 101,
OL,18,Fquoting reference 764 of 23/05/26.
OL,20,FCatch up with the latest UTV Live on
OL,21,FITVX
